{"tid":248580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（懸案公投）到底蔣介石（翻生）有冇上青樓？","createTime":"2017-05-18T16:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T06:33:43.000Z","uid":28031,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbaec30aa8ab406ad7b3d081ead24b78db29df66","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"據聞<br />\n連登救星 蔣介石（翻生）（下稱醬囝）<br />\n為成人台青樓post常客，<br />\n在追擊不法之徒同時不忘與一眾巴打分享交換各種青樓情報<br />\n如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/000411_ca12aec687bd1e5c28c4ddbca017ef33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F000411_ca12aec687bd1e5c28c4ddbca017ef33.jpg&h=64a05203&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/000412_2ab70d0f28e2482dbecbb2995bed93dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F000412_2ab70d0f28e2482dbecbb2995bed93dd.jpg&h=cd62024d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/000413_81cd620d49bf243ff7b1e86e86fbf089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F000413_81cd620d49bf243ff7b1e86e86fbf089.jpg&h=b1b458f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片取自格嚟post)<br />\n<br />\n並被金融狗打手(醬囝稱)用作人格謀殺之用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如今醬囝作出以下澄清:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/000618_6b148e62776f7104c3ca5ff6f1eb86c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F000618_6b148e62776f7104c3ca5ff6f1eb86c9.jpg&h=d82fcfcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/000619_07f273996906e59b056b3815b27cb57d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F000619_07f273996906e59b056b3815b27cb57d.jpg&h=561858dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敢問連登各位神探，醬囝到底有冇上過青樓尋歡呢？<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：蔣公(已故)都係好色之人，如今醬囝身為其後人，繼承其志獨闖青樓亦合情合理合法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：醬囝為人正直，打擊犯罪不遺餘力，點會有閒情逸致流連青樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 金融中介五毛金屬狗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070081c0ec5376f8ce53ae3833c715e922fb3e92","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"自己留翻個正皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醬囝一邊受中介狗打壓，另一邊又要重考dse以洗刷過去1分嘅往績，上青樓消遣下都好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a16c65e5fdb16c520b417abb064be87213c62b","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"推post還醬囝一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f5d5fc596b18f65158a1f5cc8f4995f2240a4f","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"三比零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdfa9b81d14bb03d095515306230e1fa959355b","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T21:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767831f072d1724c4758fcdd483ffb9d0cd2ec02","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34b918b11733e8e32fe597672d5bd5fbea4dad0","tid":248580,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"166acf6a6d758bd1c66c96b793df0e7355ceaa58","tid":248580,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"how old for the girl<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17503276be653aca2f8a3eac3c7cb9157e87768","tid":248580,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>how old for the girl<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地得一分咋你想人點啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823b3d83dcd27d1dad8a000a076d25be7e07602e","tid":248580,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:48:47.000Z","msg":"雞蟲 呢個咪放過啦"},{"pid":"c518ce2589ba70a1d31e06f1a374866dd59182f0","tid":248580,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:50:21.000Z","msg":"dse1分<br />\n人格有問題<br />\n弱智樣<br />\n雞蟲<br />\n騷擾同學<br />\n前幾日見到佢係副學士post同人討論升學<br />\n笑撚死人<br />\n得1分 中專都唔知收唔收"},{"pid":"33bb07fbd6aaac3977524604f5019a773fda3ead","tid":248580,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a62c27345570dbb840fd0a1bbd766c3d534c4814","tid":248580,"uid":104820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dse1分<br />\n人格有問題<br />\n弱智樣<br />\n雞蟲<br />\n騷擾同學<br />\n前幾日見到佢係副學士post同人討論升學<br />\n笑撚死人<br />\n得1分 中專都唔知收唔收</blockquote><br />\n點做到1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129442a229fb9c0c58ac978b64294234711d3c86","tid":248580,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T22:22:03.000Z","msg":"明知自己咁大名鼎鼎就開過個a